- cs.CV (Computer Vision): Although not explicitly mentioned in the abstract, computer vision may be used as one of the semantic elements to consider in the trajectory generation problem.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper may involve machine learning techniques to learn the effects of different combinations of semantic elements on the trajectory generation.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with the problem of generating safe trajectories for autonomous vehicles, which is a control problem.
